    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Spring does this job , Below is the notes from spring document .</p>\n<p>Below is the text from spring documentation :</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>4.Each property or constructor argument which is a value must be able to be converted from whatever format it was specified in, to the actual type of that property or constructor argument. By default Spring can convert a value supplied in string format to all built-in types, such as int, long, String, boolean, etc.</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
